Class MVCArray

java.lang.Object
com.example.dinim3akalpha001.javascript.JavascriptObject
com.example.dinim3akalpha001.javascript.object.MVCArray
public class MVCArray extends JavascriptObject
This javascript object current takes JavascriptObjects as parameters, but returns JSObjects, as it doesn't know what has been placed within it.
